%e A393635 699064 is a term since sigma(699064) = 1310760 = 1048608 + 8 + 4^9 = psi(699064) + tau(699064) + Omega(699064)^9.
%o A393635 (PARI) isok(k) = {my(f = factor(k)); sigma(f) == prod(i=1, #f~, (f[i, 1]+1) * f[i, 1]^(f[i, 2]-1)) + numdiv(f) + bigomega(f)^9; } \\ _Amiram Eldar_, Apr 13 2026
